					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">SEI/CLI has no effect on NMI. NMI is the &quot;non maskable interrupt&quot; which means specifically that you can't mask it with SEI.<br /><br />The only thing that controls whether NMI fires is the bit in $2000.<br /><br />Also, if you find that simply describing the problem to us isn't helping, consider posting a ROM.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

